# Audio file policy — DO NOT CHANGE without reading .cursor/rules/tts-audio.mdc
#
# *.mp3 are INTENTIONALLY stored as regular Git blobs (NOT LFS).
# Reason: Vercel does not fetch LFS objects during build → audio would be
# deployed as broken pointer files. Total MP3 size is small (~30 MB).
#
# WAV/OGG remain in LFS because they are source/intermediate files
# not served to production.

*.wav filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.ogg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
